highlights.text: “My Only Wish (This Year)” by Britney Spears is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 61 spots at #124.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Cruel Summer” is the highest at #30.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 187 weeks straight.
“La Diabla” by Xavi is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #74.
